    <body>
      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0040" xml:lang="de">
        <div type="envelope">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00163/" ed="1r" type="envelope"/>
          <ab hand="#hand_blue_auden" xml:lang="en">
            <lb/><hi rend="underline" hand="#hand_blue_auden">Air-Mail<space unit="char" quantity="1"/></hi>
          </ab>
          <ab hand="#hand_blue_auden" xml:lang="en">
            <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">W.H.Auden</rs>
            <address>
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">7<unclear>7</unclear> St Mark's Place
              <lb/>New York City
              <lb/>New York 10003
              <lb/>U.S.A.</rs>
            </address>
          </ab>
          <ab hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Herrn
            <lb/>Hugo Kurka</rs>
            <address>
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_356">Wien XX
              <lb/>Adalbert Stiftergasse 22/28
              <lb/><foreign xml:lang="en">Austria</foreign></rs>
            </address>   
          </ab>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00164/" ed="1v" type="envelope"/>
        </div>
        <div type="letter">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00165/" ed="2r" type="sheet"/>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <opener>
              <dateline xml:lang="en">
                <date>
                  <lb/>Nov 14<hi rend="superscript"><unclear>th</unclear></hi>
                </date>
                <placeName>
                  <address>
                    <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
                    <lb/>New York City
                    <lb/>N.Y. 10003
                    <lb/>U<unclear>.</unclear>S.A</rs>
                  </address>
                </placeName>
              </dateline>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Lieber <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Hugo</rs>:
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/>Dein Brief sehr dankend erhalten. Wie<add place="above" hand="#hand_blue_auden"> ich</add> in mein<unclear>e</unclear>
              <lb/>zweiten Brief geschriebe<unclear>n</unclear> habe, muss ich weg <gap reason="illegible" unit="char" atLeast="1" atMost="2" ana="#ana_071"/><hi rend="superscript"><unclear>t</unclear>en</hi>
              <lb/>Feb<unclear>u</unclear>ar, <del rend="overstrike" hand="#hand_blue_auden"><unclear>und</unclear> ich</del> bis 18<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi> Marz. Also für mich
              <lb/>es gibt zwei möglichkeiten .
              <seg>
                <lb/>1) <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107 #amp_person_240">Sie</rs> kommen ungefähr Jan<unclear>u</unclear>ar <foreign xml:lang="en">23<hi rend="superscript">rd</hi></foreign> , und besuchen
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_256">Christa's <unclear>S</unclear>chwester</rs> 4<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi> Febuar- <foreign xml:lang="en">11<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></foreign> und dann fliegen
                <lb/><subst><del rend="overwritten" hand="#hand_blue_auden"><unclear>r</unclear><gap reason="illegible" unit="char" atLeast="1" atMost="2"/></del><add place="superimposed" hand="#hand_blue_auden">z<unclear>u</unclear></add></subst><unclear>ru</unclear>ck nach <del rend="overstrike" hand="#hand_blue_auden">Wein</del> . <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_1">Wien</rs>.
              </seg>
              <seg>
                <lb/>2). Sie komme<unclear>n</unclear> <del rend="overstrike" hand="#hand_blue_auden">19<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi><unclear>-</unclear></del> 20<hi rend="superscript">te<unclear>n</unclear></hi> März &#x2013; 10<hi rend="superscript">te<unclear>n</unclear></hi> April .
              </seg>
              <lb/>Bitte schick mir ein Telegram welch<unclear>e</unclear> <unclear>z</unclear>eit ist
              <lb/>beque<unclear>m</unclear>er für sie beiden.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Für die Reise sie brauchen.
              <seg>
                <lb/>1) Reisepass
              </seg>
              <seg>
                <lb/>2) Certifica<unclear>t</unclear> dass sie <rs type="note" ana="#ana_070">geimpft</rs> sind .
              </seg>
              <seg>
                <lb/>3) W<unclear>a</unclear>hr<unclear>sc</unclear>heinlich ist es nicht nötig ,aber ich
                <lb/>glaube es wäre gut sein ein Einladungsbrief
                <lb/>von <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_256">Christa's Schwester</rs> zu haben, weil sie ein
                <lb/>Verwandt<unclear><subst><del rend="overwritten" hand="#hand_blue_auden"><gap reason="illegible" unit="char" quantity="1"/></del><add place="superimposed" hand="#hand_blue_auden">e</add></subst></unclear>r ist.
              </seg>
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>So fort das ich von Dich hore, schick ich
              <lb/>di<unclear>r</unclear> Fah<unclear>r</unclear>karten.
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Dein Freund
              </salute>
              <signed>
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">Wystan</rs>.
              </signed>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00166/" ed="2v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
